OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly cloudy across the
OL,6,FWestern Isles and Caithness and
OL,7,FSutherland with a few spots of light
OL,8,Frain. Elsewhere, a cloudy start but
OL,9,Fcloud breaking up to leave a dry day
OL,10,Fwith long sunny spells. Warm in the
OL,11,Fsunshine.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FMostly cloudy in the north
OL,14,Fand west overnight with isolated light
OL,15,Frain. Drier in south and east, where
OL,16,Fpatchy cloud and late evening sunshine
OL,17,Fgive way to clear spells overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
