OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FThe north and west remaining
OL,6,Fcloudy with a little light rain
OL,7,Fpossible. The south and east staying
OL,8,Fdry with more breaks in the cloud
OL,9,Fallowing more sunshine and warmer
OL,10,Ftemperatures.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMostly
OL,13,Fcloudy few days with outbreaks of
OL,14,Flight rain and drizzle, especially in
OL,15,Fthe north and west. Drier with bright
OL,16,Fand sunny intervals in south and east.
OL,17,FWinds fresher Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
